00:16:18.937 --> 00:16:21.648 position:50% align:center
[VICTOR]
This is all my fault.

00:16:21.731 --> 00:16:23.942 position:50% align:center
What have I done?

00:16:27.112 --> 00:16:29.155 position:50% align:center
[VICTOR]
