00:16:43.169 --> 00:16:47.382 position:50% align:center
[VICTOR] Also, the one
responsible for it all,

00:16:47.465 --> 00:16:50.510 position:50% align:center
was another version of myself.

00:16:52.429 --> 00:16:53.555 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:16:53.638 --> 00:16:55.098 position:50% align:center
[JUZO]
Meaning what?

00:16:55.181 --> 00:16:58.560 position:50% align:center
That you slaughtered them
while you were unconscious?

00:16:58.643 --> 00:17:00.520 position:50% align:center
[VICTOR]
It's exactly how it sounds.

00:17:00.603 --> 00:17:02.814 position:50% align:center
A sub-brain contains
a program that assists

00:17:02.897 --> 00:17:05.859 position:50% align:center
with an Extended's
functions, understand?

00:17:05.942 --> 00:17:07.819 position:50% align:center
[MARY]
Mm-hm.

00:17:07.902 --> 00:17:10.739 position:50% align:center
[VICTOR] However,
it's also a two-way street,

00:17:10.822 --> 00:17:12.198 position:50% align:center
because the user's
thought patterns

00:17:12.282 --> 00:17:15.035 position:50% align:center
can also affect how
the sub-brain operates.

00:17:15.118 --> 00:17:17.328 position:50% align:center
Incredible.

00:17:17.412 --> 00:17:19.831 position:50% align:center
[VICTOR] That's precisely
what happened to me.

00:17:19.914 --> 00:17:22.000 position:50% align:center
After seeing the carnage
on the battlefield,

00:17:22.083 --> 00:17:26.546 position:50% align:center
I was emotionally damaged, which
hurt my mental capacity as well.

00:17:27.547 --> 00:17:29.758 position:50% align:center
[VICTOR] The dual
sub-brain then took over

00:17:29.841 --> 00:17:32.927 position:50% align:center
and operated based on
the trauma I felt.

00:17:33.011 --> 00:17:34.554 position:50% align:center
Impossible.

00:17:34.637 --> 00:17:37.766 position:50% align:center
A sub-brain operating
independently?

00:17:40.226 --> 00:17:42.145 position:50% align:center
[VICTOR]
I know this is hard to believe.

00:17:42.228 --> 00:17:45.690 position:50% align:center
However, there's
no doubt in my mind.

00:17:45.774 --> 00:17:47.484 position:50% align:center
That Victor is
operating based on

00:17:47.567 --> 00:17:50.195 position:50% align:center
my thought patterns
from the battlefield.

00:17:51.321 --> 00:17:53.406 position:50% align:center
[VICTOR]
