00:17:53.490 --> 00:17:56.409 position:50% align:center
Extensions must be
purged from the world.

00:17:56.493 --> 00:17:59.829 position:50% align:center
No one can
convince him otherwise.

00:17:59.913 --> 00:18:01.039 position:50% align:center
Additionally, he believes

00:18:01.122 --> 00:18:03.375 position:50% align:center
