During the fight, that
other Victor seemed like

00:18:15.512 --> 00:18:17.931 position:50% align:center
he was more interested
looking inside Juzo

00:18:18.014 --> 00:18:19.516 position:50% align:center
than destroying him.

00:18:19.599 --> 00:18:22.686 position:50% align:center
[VICTOR] He's like
