Then the actual
reason that Victor's

00:18:39.661 --> 00:18:42.539 position:50% align:center
working alongside Spitzbergen...

00:18:42.622 --> 00:18:44.416 position:50% align:center
[VICTOR]
They both share a goal:

00:18:44.499 --> 00:18:46.584 position:50% align:center
ridding the world of Extended.

00:18:46.668 --> 00:18:48.044 position:50% align:center
[MARY gasps]

00:18:48.128 --> 00:18:51.798 position:50% align:center
[JUZO] Can't pretend I
understand, but basically,

00:18:51.881 --> 00:18:55.635 position:50% align:center
