taken over by a sub-brain.

00:18:55.719 --> 00:18:58.179 position:50% align:center
[VICTOR]
Perfectly summarized.

00:18:58.263 --> 00:19:00.640 position:50% align:center
[JUZO]
Doesn't sit well with me.

00:19:06.062 --> 00:19:08.189 position:50% align:center
[JUZO]
If that's the case,

