[JUZO]
And now there's you,

00:19:19.993 --> 00:19:22.203 position:50% align:center
controlling this
hand extension remotely

00:19:22.287 --> 00:19:24.581 position:50% align:center
from some other location.

00:19:24.664 --> 00:19:27.709 position:50% align:center
[VICTOR]
Well, the short answer is yes.

00:19:27.792 --> 00:19:29.794 position:50% align:center
[JUZO]
One thing's obvious:

00:19:29.878 --> 00:19:33.173 position:50% align:center
